response.original_title: Power Pro Lucha: A Link to the Past
response.overview: Experience the spectacle with Power Pro Lucha once again as we return for our second showing in The City of Brotherly Love on May 25, 2025!  What will the fallout be from reGeneration? What will the response from The Xyberhawx be in regard to the mauling they received from Poisynhawk? What of Max Zero and his losing streak? And what could The Spectral Envoy possibly want with Matt Mako?
response.title: Power Pro Lucha: A Link to the Past
